&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build and optimize high-quality ergonomic foundational datasets and the relevant data pipelines&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Establish data quality management processes at scale&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build analytical dashboards&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
